<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true">
<p lang="en" dir="ltr">We must keep fighting for the kind of world we want to live in. On this <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/DataPrivacyDay?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#DataPrivacyDay</a> let us all insist on action and reform for vital privacy protections. The dangers are real and the consequences are too important.</p>
