<p>I&#39;m thrilled to share that next week I&#39;ll join <a href="https://twitter.com/facebook?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@facebook</a>&#39;s incredible team as a privacy policy manager on law enforcement access and data protection issues! 1/3</p>
<p>&mdash; Robyn Greene (@Robyn_Greene) <a href="https://twitter.com/Robyn_Greene/status/1090343419237617664?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">January 29, 2019</a></p></blockquote>
