Tomorrow evening (Wednesday 1/30) at San Francisco's <a href="https://www.commonwealthclub.org/events/2019-01-30/douglas-rushkoff-team-human">Commonwealth Club</a>, I'll be interviewing longtime BB pal Douglas Rushkoff about his inspiring and (as usual) provocative new book <a href="https://rushkoff.com/books/team-human-book/">Team Human</a>! I expect a freewheeling conversation about the optimism of the cyberdelic early 1990s, why we looked to digital media as a democratizing tool to empower the individual, and how we ended up in today's (anti)social media mess. I'm hoping that the way in is the way out.
